gov.nasa.gsfc.hessi.jidl.prep.server
Class PrepServerService

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.gsfc.hessi.jidl.prep.server.PrepServerService

public class PrepServerService
extends java.lang.Object

PrepServerService is the controller class for all PrepService. For each preprocessing request, it will first checked if an instance of the appropriate PrepService already exists. If not, an InstrumentDataSet for that specific instrument is created and stored in the internal HashMap. Currently, there is only one type of PrepService in use: GenPrepService.
